Cushman Wakefield and CBRE are please to present to the market a rare opportunity to purchase a wholly leased investment in the tightly held Eagle Farm/Pinkenba precinct.
Returning $767,083.43pa true net the subject property has the following key attributes;

-  5,577sqm total GFA across two buildings
-  10,360sqm total site area
-  Leased to ASX listed Coventry Group and future ASX listed Reliance Worldwide (slated 2016)
-  WALE of 3.53 years
-  Strong review structure across both tenants of 3.5% and 3% per annum
-  Modern tilt panel buildings providing further depreciation benefits

The property is located just 8 radial kilometres from the CBD with direct access to the Gateway Motorway, Brisbane Airport, Port of Brisbane and also forms an integral part of the Australian TradeCoast Precinct.

The property is being offered for sale VIA EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST CLOSING THURSDAY 5TH MAY 2016 AT 5PM

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents, Edward Bull of CBRE and Michael Callow of Cushman & Wakefield.
